textAfterTable: 10 Songs Biography Born: 09 June 1951 in Maastricht, Netherlands Genre: Pop Years Active: '80s, '90s, '00s Dutch pop singer Benny Neyman peaked in popularity during the early to mid-'80s, and his biggest hit by far was the chart-topping single "Waarom Fluister Ik Je Naam Nog" in 1985. Born Wilhelmus Albertus Neyman on June 9, 1951, in Maastricht, Netherlands, he made his debut in 1974 but didn't score his first hit until 1980 with the Top Ten single "Ik Weet Niet Hoe."
